headline: FIS Announces Quarterly Dividend
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., October 31, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial services technology, announced a regular quarterly dividend of $0.40 per common share. The dividend is payable December 23, 2025, to FIS shareholders of record as of close of business on December 9, 2025.

headline: What Recent Developments Mean for the FIS Investment Story
summary: Fidelity National Information Services has seen its consensus analyst price target lowered from $84.39 to $83.25, signaling a modest adjustment in market expectations. This shift comes as opinions remain divided. Some analysts express optimism about the company’s improved risk/reward profile, while others cite sector headwinds and ongoing execution concerns.
